    "notes": [
      "refund application uses refund req_seq_id as the new refund transaction key and may locate the original aggregation payment by org_hf_seq_id + org_req_date",
      "the legacy internal refund request uses camelCase fields such as huifuId, merOrdId, orgReqSeqId, reqSeqId, sysId; the public gateway request maps these to snake_case data fields for this sample",
