      "refund query for a non-existing refund transaction returns resp_code=23000001 and resp_desc=原交易不存在 with an empty trade_type",
      "refund query response returns acct_split_bunch as a JSON string and includes combinedpay_fee_amt and fee_amount as top-level compatibility fields",
      "the Alipay channel refund detail is present in the refund response as aliResponseBO and is normalized to alipay_response for business-side projection"
